<L>Of Cadme wich &thorn;at was &thorn;<SUP>e</SUP> ferste man<NOTE PLACE="inter">.i. edificare</NOTE></L>
<L N="1548">That Thebes beelte<NOTE PLACE="marg">[ee: <I>later</I>]</NOTE> / or fyrst &thorn;<SUP>e</SUP> toun began</L>
