<L>Now highte I philostrate not worth a my&yogh;te<NOTE PLACE="marg">[<I>Penteo</I>, IV. 84.]</NOTE></L>
<L>Allas &thorn;ou felle Mars allas Iuno<NOTE PLACE="marg">See IV. 17.</NOTE></L>
<L N="1560">Thus hath &yogh;oure yre oure lynege fordo</L>
<L>Saue only me wrechede Palamoun</L>
