<L>And mete and drynk &thorn;is ny&yogh;t wele I brynge</L>
<L N="1616">I-nough for &thorn;<SUP>e</SUP> <I>&amp;</I> clothis for &thorn;yn beddynge</L>
<L>And &yogh;if so be &thorn;at &thorn;ou myn lady wynne</L>
