<L>And &yogh;if &thorn;ou werke wylt be good conseyl</L>
<L N="3532">I vndyrtake withoute mast or sayl</L>
<L>&YOGH;it schal I schaue here &amp; the &amp; me</L>
<L>Hast &thorn;ou not herd how sauyd was noe</L>
