<PB REF="00000119.tif" N="103"></L>
<L>And &thorn;ou wit seyn heyl maystyr Nicholay</L>
<L N="3580">Good morwe for I se &thorn;<SUP>e</SUP> wel for it is day</L>
<L>And thanne schul we be lordys al oure lyue</L>
