<DIV2 TYPE="tale">

<PB REF="00000435.tif" N="417">
<MILESTONE UNIT="6-text p" N="199">
<HEAD>[The prolog of Mellibe<MILESTONE UNIT="MS Reg. 18 C II folio" N="196b"></HEAD>
<LG TYPE="stanza">
<L>NO more of this for goddes dignite</L>
