<L>But douteles her sentence is al on<MILESTONE UNIT="MS Reg. 18 C II folio" N="197a"></L>
<L>&thorn;erfore lordynges alle [I] &yogh;ou beseche</L>
<L N="2144">&YOGH;if &thorn;at &yogh;e &thorn;inke I varye in my speche</L>
